public class PaymentEndActivity extends android.support.v7.app.AppCompatActivity
PaymentEndActivity class which is where the user will enter their payment information directly before becoming a paid member, only accessible through PaymentStartActivity. Note: Payments are not validated since we are not trying to make money off of this application.

  • Method Details

    • onCreate

      protected void onCreate(android.os.Bundle savedInstanceState)
      onCreate method that sets the visuals to payment_cardinfo.xml which is where the user enters their card info to pay. Sets EditTexts, Buttons, etc. to java variables for functionality. After the user enters their information and presses the "enter" button, their information is send to backend and they are a member.
      Overrides:
      onCreate in class android.support.v7.app.AppCompatActivity
      Parameters:
